"     (Cefaclor ER Oral)",
"    </p>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:4em;text-align:justify;\">",
"     500 mg (100): $498.00",
"    </p>",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"block mop drugH1Div\" id=\"F146874\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
"    <span class=\"drugH1\">",
"     Monitoring Parameters",
"    </span>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:0em;display:inline\">",
"     Monitor renal function. Observe for signs of anaphylaxis during first dose.",
"    </p>",
"   </div>",
